dct_title_s: Graecia vetus cum reliquis prouinciis Graecis santibus
dct_description_sm: Map of Mediterranean Sea and surrounding area, including Greece, Turkey, southern Italy and northern Africa; relief shown pictorially. From: Ioannis Meursi Operum volumen primum-[duodecimum] ... Florientiæ : regis magni Etruriae ducis typis, apud Tartinium, et Franchium, 1741-1763.
